00:12:39.190 --> 00:12:42.950
&gt;&gt; Abdullah Ibrahim: Right now,
I'm at the Hyatt [laughter],

00:12:42.950 --> 00:12:55.690 position:56%
Hyatt Regency Washington, but I have
a base with my fiancé in Germany.

00:12:55.690 --> 00:12:56.990
&gt;&gt; Dan Morgenstern: Where?

00:12:56.990 --> 00:12:58.290
&gt;&gt; Abdullah Ibrahim: Chiemsee.

00:12:58.290 --> 00:13:03.790
&gt;&gt; Dan Morgenstern:
Chiemsee is beautiful.

00:13:03.790 --> 00:13:08.370
My grandmother had a place
not far from Chiemsee.

00:13:08.370 --> 00:13:12.130
So I knew that region,
when I was a child.

00:13:12.130 --> 00:13:13.430
Yeah.

00:13:13.430 --> 00:13:16.460
&gt;&gt; Abdullah Ibrahim: Yeah
well, quite, quite beautiful.

00:13:16.460 --> 00:13:19.190
So my fiancee, Dr Marina O
Marie [assumed spelling],

00:13:19.190 --> 00:13:23.020
she's a medical doctor.

00:13:23.020 --> 00:13:27.320
And so she invited me to come

00:13:27.320 --> 00:13:30.500
because at some point I
had a illness that I had

00:13:30.500 --> 00:13:33.970
to go ahead to deal with.

00:13:33.970 --> 00:13:41.040
And through her assistance
the problem was solved.

00:13:41.040 --> 00:13:43.960
And this is one of the reasons why
I live there, the other reason was

00:13:43.960 --> 00:13:48.480
that most of the work at
that time was in Europe.

00:13:48.480 --> 00:13:51.560
So to commute from
South Africa to Europe

00:13:51.560 --> 00:13:54.700
in the Northern Hemisphere
was a bit tricky.

00:13:54.700 --> 00:14:07.430
And also, my dream in [inaudible],
of course, when European is in,

00:14:07.430 --> 00:14:13.430
you've got an instrument like
that, you have to have hope.

00:14:13.430 --> 00:14:20.440
And so Fazioli [assumed spelling]
factory, is about four hours drive

00:14:20.440 --> 00:14:22.200
from where we are [inaudible].

00:14:22.200 --> 00:14:27.020
So it's just across the border.

00:14:27.020 --> 00:14:36.260 position:56%
