buy an instrument,

00:14:45.310 --> 00:14:46.880
but now you must have
a home to put it.

00:14:46.880 --> 00:14:53.870
So that's why I'm in
Chiemsee, beautiful instrument.

00:14:53.870 --> 00:14:57.500
&gt;&gt; Dan Morgenstern: I don't
think I've ever seen one,

00:14:57.500 --> 00:15:00.680
they're not mass manufactured,
