00:15:41.460 --> 00:15:46.680
to you because you get such a
beautiful sound from the piano.

00:15:46.680 --> 00:15:50.830
You have a very special
touch and you, you know,

00:15:50.830 --> 00:15:57.860
you just create a very special kind
of feeling from that instrument.

00:15:57.860 --> 00:16:02.050
Some people use it vey precursiely,

00:16:02.050 --> 00:16:10.470
but you have a really
beautiful, almost romantic way.

00:16:10.470 --> 00:16:16.110
&gt;&gt; Abdullah Ibrahim:
Oh, thank you very much.

00:16:16.110 --> 00:16:19.710
[Inaudible] it comes,
it comes through,

00:16:19.710 --> 00:16:22.510
through trial, trial and error.

00:16:22.510 --> 00:16:35.270
Which is what, what is the best
method to, to transmit what you,

00:16:35.270 --> 00:16:37.060
what you're really feeling?

