And I wanted there because
Carnegie Hall has such great sound.

00:18:18.360 --> 00:18:19.660
&gt;&gt; Abdullah Ibrahim: Yeah.

00:18:19.660 --> 00:18:22.630
&gt;&gt; Dan Morgenstern: And
when Stan gets played there,

00:18:22.630 --> 00:18:26.300
sure thing he said,
turn off the mic.

